               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in Spitalfields-market, and a young man told me to go with him for a parcel; he<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183104070113"></xptr>went and brought this bundle - he told me to hold it while he tied his shoe; I heard a cry of Stop thief! and ran.</p>
